                    </article>

                                                                                                </div>
                        

                        <p>And don't try to tell me that Duke doesn't have the money to put on these and other events. I just got an e-mail from Brodhead telling me Duke's financial status is stable... and e-mail never lies.</p>
<p>The moral of the story is: Our parents pay a lot of money for us to come here, so let's make their visit extra special.</p>
<p>Or else we're all grounded.</p>
<p>Meeting adjourned.</p>
<p>THE CHAIRMAN hasn't seen his parents since he got that B in high school.</p>
